body: "GH-609. settings.json + schema/{types,statuses,fields,workflows}.json are single git-tracked JSON files with no merge driver; conflicting edits leave conflict markers → invalid JSON → pm silently falls back to defaults and validate reports ok:true, so governance settings/custom schema are silently lost behind a green gate. Same masking class as pm-cxyv at the config layer. Fix direction: config-integrity validate check (parse failure = hard fail) + key-level JSON merge guidance/driver."
